snippet.textDisplay: My 2 pennies: Anxiety, depression, frustration have become the norms these days in society and everyone in some form thinks and experiences the same what Abdul Hanan showed going through and than there is a time when you just cant take it anymore and  thats what Abdul Hanan expressed but the positivity in this was Old flower lady giving him a rose to reassure or give a hope to him that everything would be alright and of course than the part of Kavish was just amazing. i just wish that part was a bit longer, though they have done all with perfection but it felt too similar concept wise to 2AM , i might have gone for a female voice to make a bit different and by saying this doesnt mean Kavish werent good, they were just fantastic. People are talking about this as smooth soothing song but that isnt the feeling here.  each and every word felt so true to my heart that i really cant stop my tears everytime i listen to it. Great Job Abdul Hannan , Kavish and Cokestudio. Good luck for the rest of the season from Melbourne, Australia.
